Usage: check_bus_guides [-help] [-net_groups <list_of_net_groups>]
                        [-outFile <fileName>]

-help                                # Prints out the command usage
-net_groups <list_of_net_groups>     # To specify netgroups whose busGuides are
                                     # to be checked. Default value : *.
                                     # Example: -net_groups {ng1 ng2 ng3-*}
                                     # (string, optional)
-outFile <fileName>                  # busGuide violation log is stored in the
                                     # file specified. Default value :
                                     # checkBg.rpt (string, optional)